    "117039418": {
      "title": "Simple locally finite groups of finite Morley rank and odd type",
      "abstract": "The paper is devoted to a discussion of possible approaches to the classification of simple infinite groups of finite Morley rank. As an application of methods borrowed from finite group theory we classify locally finite simple groups of finite Morley rank with Cernikov Sylow 2-subgroups (without using the classification of finite simple groups)."
